page_0: "Looks like the battle's reached a stalemate - at least til we figures out a way to bash down their barricades. In the meantime, I've been seeing if I can find any more valuables. I know there's the pirate treasure or whatever the boss hired us for, but it can't hurt to get a little extra for myself. These guest rooms we're staying in have these nice little jewellery boxes, all silver and gemstones. Gonna take one of them to Bernard in the war room, see if he can give me a little valuation on the sly. And if he threatens to tell old Grent, well, he might be the ancient symbols expert round here, but I'm a throat-slitting expert. Just better make sure he knows that."
